Shalashar is the [[prakhutu]] for the [[overlord]] [[Ashurak]], the Slow Death. While it is a [[fiend]] native to [[Eberron]] and not a [[yugoloth]] of [[Mabar]], Shalashar nonetheless resembles an [[oinoloth]] in appearance and abilities.